data.description: Charming home in SW Atlanta! Fully renovated 3 bed/ 2 bath bungalow nestled in a quiet community located in the heart of the city. Come enjoy upgrades including a huge walk-in closet and brand new driveway. Overlook a huge backyard complete with a firepit and shed waiting for your TLC. Live your best life in Capitol View Manor where you can immerse yourself in the historic charm of the neighborhood known for its friendly community, tree-lined streets and classic architecture. This home would require low maintenance: the HVAC is 5 years old, the roof is 5 years old, and water heater is 5-6 years old as well. Walk to the Atlanta Beltline, Metropolitan Library, and Emma Millican Park. Get the best of both worlds by living in a peaceful neighborhood that is just minutes away from all that in-town living has to offer.
